body.description: Bring them sunny days, every day. No matter what the season, one liquid fabric softener delivers a daily dose of warm summer sunshine. Suavitel® Morning Sun Liquid Fabric Softener brings the optimism and positivity of a sunny day into your home, with a fresh scent that lasts and lasts. Tangerine essential oils add a citrusy brightness, with amber and musk notes that feel like a cool summer breeze. Top it off with the floral freshness of carnation and orange flower, and your clothes, family and home will be filled with a long-lasting, loving summer feeling all year round. A loving touch that lasts When it comes to your clothing, family and home, Suavitel Liquid Fabric Softener delivers a warm, loving touch that lasts. Irresistible softness and fragrances combine to create 45 days of freshness that truly smells like home. Compatible and safe to use with regular and HE washing machines, Suavitel Liquid Fabric Softener brings a loving, long-lasting freshness to your laundry and your life. For even better laundry results, pair Suavitel Liquid Fabric Softener with Suavitel Dryer Sheets for extra freshness! 50 Years of Loving Softness, Freshness & Care For decades, people have chosen Suavitel for the way it makes their laundry smell and feel - but also for how it makes them feel at home. Suavitel is more than just the sum of its parts: it’s unconditional love, bottled. Today, our fabric conditioners are accessible and affordable, responsibly made,* and are safe for all washing machines. As a brand, we care about more than your clothes - we are committed to helping you care for what you love most and helping you give your family a loving touch that lasts.
